<br>
First off, I am a parent of 4 and I smoke weed daily have done so for longer then some of u have been alive.  Those of my kids that are school age do great in school and out of school activities.  They are all clean, well dressed, and well spoken.  So no comments about bad parenting.  If so, yada yada yada, get over it.<br>
<br>
Those TV adds are all the biggest crock of stuff ever televised.  <br>
<br>
OMG, marijuana made my kid pregnant.  Marijuana don't contain sperm.  If the kid was having sex high, she would have had sex sober.  If the kid was raped (assaulted while unconcious) then thats another matter but in near 20 years of smoking weed I have seldom found any that was THAT good.  I would be willing to bet I have passed out cold more from alcohol then I ever have from weed.  Assuming I ever actually passed out from weed, which I doubt.<br>
<br>
Weed caused my accident and killed my brother.  No, u being an irresponsible driver killed your brother and u better to learn to live with that fact.  Alcohol does not cause accidents, dumb ass drivers who DECIDE to drive a car while drunk cause accidents.  Anyone who is under the influence of any substance should know better then to be behind the wheel of a car.  Is alcohol illegal cause it causes driving deaths?  No, cause the alcohol is not the cause, the driver is.  Should we ban car stereos cause some kid is fiddling with his CD player and killed his passenger brother?  No, thats ridiculous, the kid was just an irresponsible driver and it had catastrophic results.  The same can be said for every DUI death in history.  <br>
<br>
Father searches kids room...  Why would a father do that?    Lets say he found something he shouldnt have.  Well, he confirmed what he already knew.  Was that confirmation worth the breach in trust and privacy?  Why not just eliminate the middleman, assume the worst, and confront the problem with the kid.  If the kid still isn't being honest then at least u still sat him/her down and told the kid how u feel about the situation.  Lets say the father found nothing in his search.  How do u explain to the kid, or yourself for that matter, that ensuring that your child never trusts u again is justified?<br>
<br>
Weed supports terrorism.  Easy answer, legalize marijuana.  That way, weed supports the good guys.  Win/win.  But u say weed is bad it cant be legal.  Weed is worse then alcohol/tobacco it cant be legal.  Maybe you are right, maybe weed is this horrible thing.  But I tell u what, if u send a kid out with 10 bucks and tell him to bring u a dime bag he will bring u back a dime bag.  Send the same kid out with 10 bucks and tell him to get u a 6er of Budweisers and a pack of Marlboro's the kid will come back and tell u to buy your own damn beer.  I dont care what anyone tells you, it is easier to buy drugs on the street then booze from the store.  Drug dealers dont card u.  Stores should be carding near everyone these days considering the penalties for selling to a minor.<br>
